post_text: ELCO Commencement 2020
text:
ELCO Commencement 2020

YOUTUBE.COM
ELCO Commencement 2020

post_text:
The ELCO School District Building Offices will reopen beginning on Monday, June 15th for summer hours.

Summer office hours are Monday-Thursday from 7:00AM - 3:00PM with a 30-minute lunch closing from 12:00Noon-12:30PM.

Due to construction, the High School Office will be located in the High School Library and can be accessed by parking in the District Office parking lot and using the same walkway normally used to enter the District Office. The High School Library entrance is located on the right side of the walkway.

The automated phone system, voice mailbox, and the elcocovid email addressed used during the school shut down has been disabled. All communication to the school should resume in the manner used prior to the school shutdown on March 13, 2020.
text:
The ELCO School District Building Offices will reopen beginning on Monday, June 15th for summer hours.

Summer office hours are Monday-Thursday from 7:00AM - 3:00PM with a 30-minute lunch closing from 12:00Noon-12:30PM.

Due to construction, the High School Office will be located in the High School Library and can be accessed by parking in the District Office parking lot and using the same walkway normally used to enter the District Office. The High School Library entrance is located on the right side of the walkway.

The automated phone system, voice mailbox, and the elcocovid email addressed used during the school shut down has been disabled. All communication to the school should resume in the manner used prior to the school shutdown on March 13, 2020.
